trans-unit.source: The NamedImagesCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> objects, which are objects that have an associated image and a name that is unique to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Klassen NamedImagesCollection representerar en mängd <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objekt, som är objekt som har en associerad avbildning och ett namn som är unik för samlingen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: This class is exposed as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property of the root <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> object, and is only available at run time.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen exponeras som den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>samlingsegenskapen av roten <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>objekt och är endast tillgänglig vid körning.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>

trans-unit.source: An image can be any object derived from the .NET Framework <xref:System.Drawing.Image> class, such as <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>, which is created dynamically.
trans-unit.target: En bild kan vara ett objekt som härletts från .NET Framework <xref:System.Drawing.Image>class, till exempel <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>, som skapas dynamiskt.</xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> </xref:System.Drawing.Image>

trans-unit.source: The image can be stored in this collection, and then assigned at a later time to any image property in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control, such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Bilden kan lagras i den här samlingen och sedan tilldelas vid ett senare tillfälle att alla image-egenskapen i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontroll, till exempel <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: When one of the image properties in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control is set by specifying a `string` value, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property, of type NamedImagesCollection, is first checked to see if an image with that name exists.
trans-unit.target: När en av dess egenskaper i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontrollen anges genom att ange en `string` värde, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>samlingsegenskapen av typen NamedImagesCollection, kontrolleras först om det finns en bild med det namnet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is found, this image is used.
trans-unit.target: Om matchande <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objektet hittades, den här avbildningen används.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is not located, the string expression is treated as a URL, image resource name or pathname.
trans-unit.target: Om matchande <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objektet finns inte, stränguttryck behandlas som en URL, resurs avbildningsnamn eller pathname.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>
